# Cybersecurity Threat Detection

This collection focuses on **Protecting financial infrastructure from DDoS attacks, phishing, and unauthorized access.**.

## Notebooks

- 01_ddos_attack_detection_network_traffic.ipynb
- 02_phishing_email_classification_nlp.ipynb
- 03_unauthorized_access_behavioral_biometrics.ipynb
- 04_zero_day_threat_anomaly_detection.ipynb
- 05_malware_file_signature_clustering.ipynb
- 06_endpoint_security_event_scoring.ipynb
